snippet.title: La Dispute - Pilgrimage Trailer
snippet.description:
Discover the music and lyrics of La Dispute's 'Panorama' as you wander on a pilgrimage through a digital fantasy landscape from Joost Eggermont and Jorrit De Vries

Download now at https://ladispute.org/pilgrimage

Pilgrimage is available for free download, but you have the option to pay what you want as a donation to charity. All proceeds benefit The Trevor Project - http://www.thetrevorproject.org

Game design & development by:
Joost Eggermont
Jorrit De Vries

Available for Mac & PC

Official Site: https://www.ladispute.org/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/LaDisputeMusic/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/ladisputeband
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/la_dispute/
Spotify: https://spoti.fi/2QcGTEW

#ladispute #panorama #epitaph
